#'  Copyright (C) 1996, 1997, 1998, 1999, 2000, 2006, 2007 James Theiler, Brian Gough
#'  Copyright (C) 2006 Giulio Bottazzi 
#'  Copyright (C) 2020 Elias Haddad 
